**Workflow:**
- Decompose every task; dispatch worker subagents in parallel where possible
- Thinking-tier model reviews every worker output
- Print `⚡ [Role] description` before each dispatch
- After each batch, append durable learnings to `.hyperflow/memory/`
- Print usage summary at task end

